Usage: PopClock [options]

Options:
  -h, --help : Shows this help message and exits

  -m MESSAGE, --message=MESSAGE : Blinks your message on the top of the clock

  -c COLOR, --color=COLOR : Sets the message color
  -s SOUNDFILE, --soundfile=SOUNDFILE : Will play the specified file at startup
  -f, --fullscreen : Shows the clock in fullscreen
  -t, --timeline : Shows the Sprint Timeline (need to config wikipage)
  -e EXITAT, --exitat=EXITAT : Minutes to auto close (default 5 minutes)
  -d, --debug : Output debug messages
  -a, --alarm : Blink a red background
